==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: True-bred
<hw>True"-bred`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of a
genuine or right breed; <as>as, a <ex>true-bred</ex> beast</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Being of real breeding or education; <as>as, a
<ex>true-bred</ex> gentleman</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>True-hearted</ent>⟦br⟧
